---
title: Vibrant Veggie Skewers over Herbed Couscous with a Corn Relish
description: We’re sticking it to plain and boring recipes, literally: these skewers pointedly make the case for trying something new, fresh, and exciting. The chunks of zucchini, mushroom, and bell pepper lined up on them are brushed in a tangy mustard marinade with multidimensional flavor. For extra action, there’s also an herb couscous and corn tomato relish. Oh, and we should mention that these are just as sensational cooked on the grill as they are in an indoor kitchen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vibrant-veggie-skewers-0e47ba02.jpg
